<HI>ROXANA:</HI> OR, THE FORTUNATE MISTRESS.</P>
<P>BEING A HISTORY OF 'THE LIFE AND Va&s;t Variety of FORTUNES OF <HI>Mademoi&s;elle de Beleau.</HI></P>
<P>LONDON, Printed for</P>
<P>H. SLATER, in <HI>Clements Inn.</HI></P>
